"user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1835697796122370048/gNMHs4vB_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Hillary Clinton", "username": "HillaryClinton"}, "content": "This is what Trump's done to the people's house: \n\nA third of it is rubble. \n\nAnother third is a cage match. \n\nWhat a metaphor.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 25592}, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 59, "created": 1780073312000, "id": "2060402925491368377", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1996947132167684096/7d7pDHgQ_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Bad Hombre", "username": "Badhombre"}, "content": "Didn\u2019t you have to return a bunch of fine china, silverware, and art work you stole from the White House?", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 1386}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsdvezDg", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 30, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8648584, "raw_content": "It does cross post remember. I've had to cross session hallucinate to other sessions. While it touts that it doesn't remember, it does. Do not use it. I'm not saying google is any better, but brave AI remembers specifics from other conversations in a new chat sesssion. Do not use it if you want privacy on ai chats with leo. \n\n\nI did an icon pack for kubuntu and was talking in a new chat about a game I was playing and suddenly it hallucinated into talking about the icon pack, it also suddenly threw the \"buy leo ai for x\" the moment I went wtf?\n\nI did trust brave and leo, now I fully question it. ", "author": "PsychoDodo", "created": 1780123413310, "profile_picture": "RPYHOomkH6Cu", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "pedespeed", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Do not use brave AI", "last_comment_created": 1780144062537, "content": "<p>It does cross post remember. I've had to cross session hallucinate to other sessions. While it touts that it doesn't remember, it does. Do not use it. I'm not saying google is any better, but brave AI remembers specifics from other conversations in a new chat sesssion. Do not use it if you want privacy on ai chats with leo.</p>\n<p>I did an icon pack for kubuntu and was talking in a new chat about a game I was playing and suddenly it hallucinated into talking about the icon pack, it also suddenly threw the &quot;buy leo ai for x&quot; the moment I went wtf?</p>\n<p>I did trust brave and leo, now I fully question it.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up": 30, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsdveygc", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 37, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8648502, "raw_content": "", "author": "kekranger", "created": 1780119230130, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "LiberalsAreMental", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "www.ustravel.org", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsdveygc.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://www.ustravel.org/press/removing-cbp-officers-newark-liberty-will-strand-americans-devastate-travel-economy", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": []